metadata.description: The Tiki Pigz are on the rampage!! This collection of 2,000 mischievous animals roam around the jungle and make amazing Tiki pets! Ancient explorers would tell stories of the mysterious island of Moecca, a lost world far beyond the horizon filled with strange secrets waiting to be discovered! The island will become an immersive world explored through a gamified roadmap where milestone progress is driven by community achievement.
metadata.name: Pig #0001
